display flex : d-flex 
align-items  : align-items-center 

(1) input type : text, date, password, number, email
    textarea
class : form-control 

(2) label : 
class : form-label

(3) for radio button & checkbox : 
class : form-check-input 

(4) for radio button & checkbox label:
class : form-check-label  

(5) for radio button & checkbox parent div :
class : form-check  
if set inline class : form-check-inline 

(6) for range :
    class form-range 

(7) for dropdown : class : form-select

(8) to join button or label end of input use 
    parent : input-group 
    child : input-group-text

(9) floating labels :
    parent  : form-floating
    if we want floating labels in input use placeholder complusory.
    if we remove or not set the label are show as static.
